body.h1: PKPD model for methacetin based liver function tests.
body.p: This model is a physiological pharmacokinetic/pharmacodynamics model (PKPD) for the absorption, distribution, metabolism and elimination of methacetin, bicarbonate and paracetamol encoded in SBML format.
body.div: The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort.
This file has been created by Matthias Koenig.
